Notes: WIAC Tournament Semifinal...SP advances to title game for first-time ever and
will host UW-Oshkosh Sat. at time TBA...SP lost at home in semifinals past
three years...SP's Nechuta had 20 of her 24 points in second half...SP closed
first half with 10-0 run...Schmitt fourth SP player this year to hit 1,000 pts
